00:24.339 --> 00:26.374
I've seen the true face
of terrorism.

00:26.775 --> 00:29.176
And in 2016,
when America experienced

00:29.178 --> 00:31.312
multiple domestic
terrorist attacks,

00:31.612 --> 00:34.480
my good friend and New York
firefighter, Tim Brown,

00:34.482 --> 00:36.818
came to me with a movie concept.

00:37.385 --> 00:40.123
Based around the idea,
what would happen

00:40.455 --> 00:43.157
if simultaneous terrorist
attacks occurred

00:43.159 --> 00:45.628
all across America,
all on one day.

00:46.262 --> 00:47.463
What would that look like?

00:48.162 --> 00:50.463
I didn't even like thinking
about the possibility of that

00:50.465 --> 00:52.768
and the bigger question
that came to my mind was,

00:53.436 --> 00:54.571
could we prevent it?

00:55.370 --> 00:56.638
Like Jason said,

00:56.971 --> 00:59.541
I sifted through the rubble
of the Oklahoma City bombing.

00:59.809 --> 01:02.575
I was under the towers
when they came down in New York,

01:02.577 --> 01:04.346
killing 93 of my friends.

01:04.679 --> 01:06.781
I've seen terrorism
up close and personal.

01:07.783 --> 01:09.683
So I thought what if
we banded together,

01:09.685 --> 01:13.622
not just to raise awareness
of terrorism in America,

01:14.122 --> 01:16.689
but to actually
help Americans understand

01:16.691 --> 01:18.391
how to prevent it,

01:18.393 --> 01:22.598
how to prevent this scourge
from visiting us, this evil

01:22.831 --> 01:25.267
of... from doing
what it did to me.

01:26.301 --> 01:27.534
And I didn't have to think twice

01:27.536 --> 01:29.437
about being involved
in this project.

01:29.637 --> 01:31.638
To raise awareness
for all Americans,

01:31.640 --> 01:34.242
to understand that this
a very real threat.

01:34.610 --> 01:35.911
And how they can prevent it.

01:36.479 --> 01:39.346
And Tim went about
recruiting 9/11 survivors

01:39.348 --> 01:40.814
to be involved in this film.

01:40.816 --> 01:43.883
And I... I went about looking
for fellow veterans

01:43.885 --> 01:46.589
and families of the fallen
from all wars,

01:46.822 --> 01:49.324
so that we could show you
how we can prevent

01:49.592 --> 01:51.293
a possible real story

01:51.760 --> 01:53.194
from ever happening.

01:54.363 --> 01:57.197
I hope when you watch this
you will spread the word

01:57.199 --> 01:59.299
to all your friends
and fellow Americans

01:59.301 --> 02:00.303
about this threat,

02:00.670 --> 02:01.837
