in school a little bit.

40:04.184 --> 40:05.218
Yeah.

40:05.618 --> 40:08.588
Did they tell you
anything about why,

40:09.055 --> 40:10.923
what happened, what caused it?

40:11.191 --> 40:12.225
No?

40:12.825 --> 40:13.894
Uh,

40:14.093 --> 40:15.961
kind of interesting um,

40:16.196 --> 40:18.129
my grandson
had the same reaction

40:18.131 --> 40:21.501
when I asked him
that same situation, um.

40:22.568 --> 40:25.238
You know about the two towers
that were hit?

40:26.439 --> 40:28.809
But did you know
that there were four planes?

40:29.475 --> 40:32.546
Mm-hmm.
