40:41.220 --> 40:42.255
And...

40:42.856 --> 40:46.126
that was where the term came,
it's time to roll.

40:47.093 --> 40:48.859
Do you recall hearing
that statement?

40:48.861 --> 40:49.829
No?

40:50.229 --> 40:51.263
Well...

40:52.097 --> 40:56.869
this is a dedication,
a tribute, to honor

40:57.738 --> 41:01.707
those more than 3,000 people
