41:01.709 --> 41:04.678
Civilians, workers,
first responders,

41:04.977 --> 41:07.914
uh and subsequently since then,

41:08.515 --> 41:10.518
um, almost 7,000...

41:12.551 --> 41:14.787
military men and women
have been killed,

41:15.555 --> 41:16.623
in what is known

41:17.189 --> 41:20.660
as the War on Terrorism
since September 11th.

41:27.100 --> 41:28.935
I think I want to join
the military.

41:30.636 --> 41:31.905
